OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be
OL,6,Fcloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with outbreaks of light rain
OL,8,Fpossible, mainly in the west. The best
OL,9,Fof the drier spells in the east.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,12,Foccasional outbreaks of light rain.
OL,13,FRain mainly in the west with the best
OL,14,Fof the drier and brighter spells in
OL,15,Fthe east.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FMainly
OL,18,Fcloudy, patchy rain on Tuesday, some
OL,19,Fbright spells. Wednesday and Thursday
OL,20,Fwill be dry with sunny spells and
OL,21,Fbecoming very warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
